reviewText:
Peach dvd is this oddball distributor that puts out dvd's
usually with previously licensed footage or they make they own with
somewhat known C-List Stars (They used WCW's Major Guns) with a number of there videos

There content  is usually just middle of the road so/so late night tv stuff
Save your money and buy Janine's real videos!

The only part of this I was disappointed in was Janine's strip segment.  The video is titled with her name but in her strip scene she never even removes her g-string!  What's up with that?!  Certainly not me!  That's the only real cheat in this video, but it's a big cheat since she is the title model.  I only gave it four stars because of this.

Its worth the few bucks i paid for it! I like pretty girls! So what if there is no sexual content. If you want that sort of thing go to an adult store. While this is not a wholesome video, there is enough nudity for the eye and imagination. One of the best things about this dvd is that there is not one naked man on the whole thing! Cudos!
